{"version":"1.2","person":{"datePublished":"2023-12-20","name":"Raymond III de Narbonne-Pelet","nameForms":[{"lang":"fr","fullText":"Raymond III de Narbonne-Pelet","parts":[{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Given","value":"Raymond III"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Surname","value":"de Narbonne-Pelet"}],"order":"EUROTYPIC"}],"gender":"Male","lifespan":"1075–1140","fullLifespan":"environ 1075–environ 1140","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/bzcfm/thumb200s.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"memoryArtifacts":[{"memoryType":"PHOTO","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7777-114885-14351-98/dist.png?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/142933288","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7777-114885-14351-98/thumb200s.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","deepZoomUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/deepzoomcloud/dzpatron/v1/TH-7777-114885-14351-98/scale?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","headline":"Sample of a medieval fur cloak worn over chainmail","@type":"ImageObject"}],"birthDate":"+1075","birthPlace":{"address":"Alès, Gard, Occitanie, France","geo":{"latitude":44.1274,"longitude":4.079,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"deathDate":"+1140","deathPlace":{"address":"Narbonne, Aude, Occitanie, France","geo":{"latitude":43.1838,"longitude":2.9963,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"userCertifiedLifeSummary":"Armoirie de la famille Narbonne Pelet : Pelet De gueules (Narbonne) à un écusson d'argent au chef de sable (Melgueil) Raymond 1er de Narbonne-Pelet Croisé Seigneur d'Alès L’appel à la croisade, adressé surtout à la noblesse du sud de la Loire, d’où eﬆ issu Urbain II, dépasse largement ce cadre : aux Provençaux s’ajoutent Godefroy de Bouillon, duc de Basse-Lotharingie, et son frère Baudouin de Boulogne, Hugues de Vermandois, frère du roi Philippe 1er de France, avec des chevaliers français et champenois et le groupe conduit par Robert II de Normandie et Étienne de Blois. Le départ eﬆ fixé au 15 août 1095. Il se marie avec Agnès des Baux (1080-1140) fille de Guillaume Hugues des Baux (1055-1110) et de Vierne de Posquières (-1110). Ils eurent : 1) Bernard II (1110-1171)Comte de Melgueil (34) Co-seigneur d'Alès (30) 1110-1171 Marié en 1145 avec Béatrice de Melgueil, Comtesse de Melgueil (34) (1125-1190) ; 2) Rixende de Narbonne-Pelet (1120-1171) Mariée en 1140 avec Aymar Ier de Poitiers-Valentinois (1122-1188), Comte de Valentinois ;\n\nrelevé JPR Teyssier Chalancon Mangas, Verger, Lecomte","sourceList":[{"title":"Wikipedia - the Surcoat or Pelet/Pilat","sourceType":"DEFAULT","sourceLink":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surcoat","sourceUri":"3VDF-94Q"},{"title":"Wikipedia -Raymond \"Pelet\" de Narbonne","sourceType":"DEFAULT","sourceLink":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raymond_Pilet_d%27Alès","sourceUri":"3VDX-KN7"}],"events":[{"name":"Birth","sources":"0","year":"1075","date":"environ 1075","place":"Alès, Gard, Occitanie, France"},{"name":"Death of Parent","sources":"0","year":"1080","date":"1080","age":"5","id":"GN83-QBB"},{"name":"Marriage","sources":"0","year":"1109","date":"environ 1109","place":"Narbonne, Aude, Occitanie, France","type":"Spousal","age":"34","id":"KHQN-GBK"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1110","date":"du environ 1110 au 1130","place":"Narbonne, Aude, Occitanie, France","age":"55","id":"LC5K-PYB"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1120","date":"environ 1120","place":"Alès, Gard, Occitanie, France","age":"45","id":"GXQR-RNJ"},{"name":"Death of Spouse","sources":"0","year":"1140","date":"1140","place":"Narbonne, Aude, Occitanie, France","age":"65","id":"KHQN-GBK"},{"name":"Death","sources":"0","year":"1140","date":"environ 1140","place":"Narbonne, Aude, Occitanie, France","age":"65"}],"parent":[{"name":"Bernard de Narbonne-Pelet Ier","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1050–1080","birthDate":"+1050","deathDate":"+1080","age":